<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Wild Mushroom Conserve</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal">Probably the greatest wild mushroom pickle/preserve you will ever taste. 
Yield: 1 qt canning jar </div>
